837615518.text: "TACE and ADAM17 protein and protease activity were up-regulated markedly at 10 h and maintained to 40 h. Treatment of COCs with the TACE and ADAM17 selective inhibitor TNFalpha processing inhibitor-2 (TAPI-2) significantly suppressed in a time dependent manner downstream targets of EGF receptor activation such as ERK1/2 phosphorylation, Ptgs2, Has2, and Tnfaip6 mRNA expression, hormone induced COC expansion, and meiotic maturation of the oocytes."
